{"tid":1287784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果唔想下一代變成(BBC揭2000新疆兒童進「再教育營」 學校建電流圍欄)","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:54:35.000Z","uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dbecd3063e6c81f0d6371d8b627dfa88e1ed87d7","tid":1287784,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"繼新疆再教育營後，英國廣播公司(BBC)今日的報道指，中國在新疆大規模建寄宿學校，自去年4月，已將維吾爾自治區附近的葉城縣2000名穆斯林兒童送入寄宿學校，接受再教育。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n報道指兒童在宿寄學校內會被嚴格隔離封閉管理，許多學校都有覆蓋全校的監控及警報系統，更設有1萬伏特電圍欄。學生在校內不能說中文以外的語言，如使用維吾爾語或其他當地語言，會受罰。而單在新疆南部，中國政府已投入了12億美元，不斷擴建類似學校。<br />\n<br />\n今次運動一輸中共一定玩呢隻"},{"pid":"3215e4b6a0541208c30407e232fc53b3318cee0d","tid":1287784,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}